          "uuid": "34bfa834-39cb-4a1b-b4b5-c81c0ba0bb95",
          "text": "At January 3, 2020, the Company had state net operating losses of $77 million and state tax credits of $7 million. Both will begin to expire in fiscal 2020; however, the Company expects to utilize $24 million and $7 million of these state net operating losses and state tax credits, respectively. The Company also had foreign net operating losses of $44 million, which do not expire. The Company expects to utilize $9 million of these foreign net operating losses.",
